    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This car is in poor condition. The exterior has significant wear, including noticeable dents, scratches, and cosmetic damage. The interior shows heavy use with worn seating, damaged trim, and general deterioration. Mechanically, the car has issues that will require attention and repair before reliable use. Suitable for buyers comfortable with a project vehicle or those needing basic transportation with the expectation of repairs.",
